# Version-control .claude/skills/ (the shared LLM-deployment skills) while
# keeping every other .claude/ entry (personal settings, worktrees, memory,
# IDE config) local and untracked. `!.claude/` also guards against
# environments that globally ignore .claude/ (e.g. a ~/.gitignore_global rule).
!.claude/
.claude/*
!.claude/skills/

# make artifacts
CMakeFiles/
CMakeCache.txt
cmake_install.cmake
platforms/scripts/env_config
platforms/scripts/br_config

# build artifacts
*.cmd
*.jou
*.log
*.xsa
.Xil
.ipcache
bootgen_log.txt
final_vck5000.pdi
_x
vck5000_aie_base_graph_hw.ltx
vck5000_aie_base_graph_hw.xsa.link_summary
Work
build
build_*
build-xrt
install
install-xrt
platform_repo
myproj
sw_comp
sd_card
sysroot
components
air_project
__pycache__/
sandbox

# build results
libadf.a
*.elf
*.elf.*
CLAUDE.md

# documents
*.pdf
